ABOUT US

HISTORY - VISION - MISSION

&

UNIGEM'S MAIN BUSINESS ACTIVITIES

UNIGEM Co., Ltd. was founded by Ms. Nguyen Thi Bich Ngoc, a young entrepreneur who started her business in various fields such as agricultural import-export, construction and interior design, real estate, etc. During a business trip to Thailand, she discovered beautiful and rare colored gemstones at a gem fair and fell in love with them. These captivating colored gemstones became her passion, and she began to study and collect gemstones at that time.

When her passion for gemstones grew, she immersed herself in gemology and jewelry design. After more than 2 years of studying and developing her knowledge and skills, combined with her keen business acumen, she discovered that Vietnam has many beautiful gemstone mines, and the Vietnamese market is still very potential and fresh. Notable large gemstone mines include high-quality Spinel, Sapphire, and Ruby in Luc Yen. Ruby mines in Nghe An, Sapphire in Phan Thiet, Aquamarine in Thanh Hoa, Peridot in Gia Lai... Therefore, gemstone prices in Vietnam are very competitive compared to the world. Seeing the potential and advantages of this new field, she started her business from 2021 to the present.

UNIGEM only deals in natural gemstone products, accompanied by certificates confirming they are completely natural and untreated, such as Aquamarine, Morganite, Heliodor, Tourmaline, Emerald, Ruby, Spinel, Sapphire, Peridot, Garnet... sourced from both Vietnam and international imports.

Additionally, UNIGEM has a young, enthusiastic, dynamic, and creative team. Notably, the jewelry design team is youthful, and Ms. Bich Ngoc herself is a professionally trained jewelry designer who is always passionate and focused on creating unique, novel designs to produce distinctive jewelry pieces that reflect the individual personality of their owners.

UNIGEM carries a special meaning, intended by its founder: "Unique Gemstone" Each gemstone is unique, no two stones are alike, just as each of us is one of a kind in this world. Every stone tells a story, as they have gone through millions of years of formation and refinement to achieve the colors and sparkling transparency we see today.

With the vision of bringing Vietnamese gemstones to the international market, which is also UNIGEM's vision for the period from 2021 to 2030. Bringing foreign currency to the country and promoting our nation's rich and beautiful natural resources.

With passion and intense love for beauty, feng shui, and energy, the gemstones selected and displayed in our store always achieve near-absolute purity. Our designed products undergo rigorous inspection processes to ensure that each piece of natural gemstone jewelry not only harmonizes with feng shui principles but also serves as an elegant, fashionable piece with lasting value.

Throughout our business operations in Vietnam, UNIGEM has built a reputation and gained a loyal customer base who trust and support our products. The company's management sincerely thanks our valued customers for choosing UNIGEM's products during this time. We commit to maintaining quality while continuously developing our strengths and improving our products and services to deliver the best experiences for customers who have placed their trust in us.

Once again, we sincerely appreciate and value our customers' trust in UNIGEM.

Best regards./.